Notes: Tag slips down to right flipper and moves across belly to left side. VGB clearly seen.  Nice flipper views.  Black dot is fish (Vid 53, 26:27:00).  UTC offset on video had been set to -2 (so off by 4 hours).
PRH_Notes: Added 4 hours to video times, added 1.5314 to Depth variable to account for tag that doesn't break the surface.  pc was adjusted to account for the adjustment.

Notes: Western part of ptrack may be inaccurate because whale is sleeping/coasting during day. Feeding happening at night!
PRH_Notes: Adjusted pressure by adding 2.1701, also changed pconst
